OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772062282
OL,3,C#24 million airport upgrade plans
OL,4,Capproved
OL,6,FGuernsey politicians have approved a
OL,7,F#24 million upgrade to Alderney's
OL,8,Fdilapidated runway.
OL,10,FA project like this was signed off on
OL,11,Fby Deputies over three years ago, but
OL,12,Fit was eventually scrapped as costs
OL,13,Fballooned to #37 million following a
OL,14,Ftender process.
OL,16,FThe new Chief Minister, Deputy Lindsay
OL,17,Fde Sausmarez, then committed to
OL,18,Finvesting in the island's
OL,19,Finfrastructure "at the lowest possible
OL,20,Fcost without cutting corners on things
OL,21,Flike safety or regulatory standards".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
