PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772062282
OL,3,C#24 million airport upgrade plans
OL,4,Capproved
OL,6,FThe revised plans include resurfacing
OL,7,Fwork, updating lighting and drainage,
OL,8,Fand widening the asphalt runway from
OL,9,F18 to 23 metres.
OL,11,FHowever, unlike previous proposals,
OL,12,Fthe runway will not be extended and a
OL,13,Fnew terminal will not be built.
OL,15,FConstruction will start in April 2027
OL,16,Fand is scheduled to finish by December.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/3
