CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772062282
OL,3,C#24 million airport upgrade plans
OL,4,Capproved
OL,6,FThere will be major disruption to air
OL,7,Ftravel to and from Alderney, with the
OL,8,Fairport expected to close for up to
OL,9,Ffive months - although ITV News
OL,10,Funderstands medical evacuations will
OL,11,Fcontinue throughout via helicopter and
OL,12,Fboat.
OL,14,FThe news will be cautiously welcomed
OL,15,Fby Alderney residents, with many
OL,16,Fgrowing increasingly frustrated at the
OL,17,Flack of progress.
